<subSubSection id="A7CC2DBDFFC9FFE2FF8DFECEFD17FD8F" pageId="19" pageNumber="294" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="EF697E36FFC9FFE2FF8DFECEFD17FD8F" blockId="19.[113,1089,296,607]" pageId="19" pageNumber="294">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFC9FFE2FF8DFECEFF5EFE8F" bold="true" box="[113,224,296,319]" pageId="19" pageNumber="294">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="8B4703C7FFC9FFE2FF1AFECEFE26FE8F" author="BOHEMAN" box="[230,408,296,319]" firstAuthor="BOHEMAN" pageId="19" pageNumber="294" refId="ref47930" refString="BOHEMAN C. H. 1854: Monographia Cassididarum. Tomus Secundus. Officina Norstedtiana, Holmiae, 506 pp. + 2 pls." type="book" year="1854">BOHEMAN (1854)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFC9FFE2FDF6FECEFD41FE8F" authorityName="Boheman" authorityYear="1854" box="[522,767,296,319]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Chelymorpha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="294" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ignobilis">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFC9FFE2FDF6FECEFD41FE8F" box="[522,767,296,319]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="294">Chelymorpha ignobilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from ZMHB material. 
<bibRefCitation id="8B4703C7FFC9FFE2FC0BFECEFF7BFEEF" author="SPAETH" firstAuthor="SPAETH" pageId="19" pageNumber="294" pagination="715 - 732" refId="ref50857" refString="SPAETH F. 1909 a: Kritische Studien uber Chelymorpha Boh. und die verwandten Gattungen (Col.). Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift 1909: 715 - 732." type="journal article" year="1909" yearSuffix="a">SPAETH (1909a)</bibRefCitation>
proposed for this species the genus 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFC9FFE2FDBFFEAEFCEEFEEF" authority="Spaeth, 1909" authorityName="Spaeth" authorityYear="1909" box="[579,848,328,351]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Exestastica" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="294" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFC9FFE2FDBFFEAEFD02FEEF" box="[579,700,328,351]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="294">Exestastica</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="8B4703C7FFC9FFE2FD3FFEAEFCEEFEEF" author="Spaeth" box="[707,848,328,351]" firstAuthor="Spaeth" journalOrPublisher="Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift" pageId="19" pageNumber="294" pagination="715 - 732" part="1909" refId="ref50857" refString="SPAETH F. 1909 a: Kritische Studien uber Chelymorpha Boh. und die verwandten Gattungen (Col.). Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift 1909: 715 - 732." title="Kritische Studien uber Chelymorpha Boh. und die verwandten Gattungen (Col.)" type="journal article" year="1909">Spaeth, 1909</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, however, pointed that the specimen he used for description did not fully agree with the original description of 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFC9FFE2FBD4FE8EFF70FE2F" authorityName="Boheman" authorityYear="1854" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Chelymorpha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="294" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ignobilis">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFC9FFE2FBD4FE8EFF70FE2F" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="294">C. ignobilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but with additional specimens identified as that species in various collections. BOROWIEC (1999a) synonymized 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFC9FFE2FE48FE4EFCE4FE0F" authority="Wagener, 1877" authorityName="Wagener" authorityYear="1877" box="[436,858,424,447]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Hybosa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="294" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="margineguttata">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFC9FFE2FE48FE4EFD0FFE0F" box="[436,689,424,447]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="294">Hybosa margineguttata</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="8B4703C7FFC9FFE2FD45FE4EFCE4FE0F" author="Wagener" box="[697,858,424,447]" firstAuthor="Wagener" pageId="19" pageNumber="294" pagination="49 - 79" refId="ref52211" refString="WAGENER B. 1877: Cassididae. Mittheilungen des Munchner Entomologischen Vereins 1: 49 - 79." type="journal article" year="1877">Wagener, 1877</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
with 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFC9FFE2FC66FE4EFBA8FE0F" authorityName="Boheman" authorityYear="1854" box="[922,1046,424,447]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Chelymorpha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="294" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ignobilis">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFC9FFE2FC66FE4EFBA8FE0F" box="[922,1046,424,447]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="294">E. ignobilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but he was not able to locate the type of the latter in the ZMHB collection. During my stay in ZMHB I was also unable to trace the type of 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFC9FFE2FDACFE0EFD74FE4F" authorityName="Boheman" authorityYear="1854" box="[592,714,488,511]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Chelymorpha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="294" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ignobilis">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFC9FFE2FDACFE0EFD74FE4F" box="[592,714,488,511]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="294">E. ignobilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and I thus follow Spaethʼs concept of the species. I studied the 
<typeStatus id="306DC094FFC9FFE2FE6FFDEEFE4EFDAF" box="[403,496,520,543]" pageId="19" pageNumber="294">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFC9FFE2FDEDFDEEFD7BFDAF" authorityName="Boheman" authorityYear="1855" box="[529,709,520,543]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Hybosa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="294" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="indecens">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFC9FFE2FDEDFDEEFD7BFDAF" box="[529,709,520,543]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="294">Hybosa indecens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and found that it is conspecific with 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFC9FFE2FF8DFDCEFF52FD8F" authorityName="Boheman" authorityYear="1854" box="[113,236,552,575]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Chelymorpha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="294" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ignobilis">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFC9FFE2FF8DFDCEFF52FD8F" box="[113,236,552,575]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="294">E. ignobilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and I therefore synonymize both species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
